text.section:
The consumer members:
Shall be members of the general public;
May not be or ever have been an acupuncturist or in training to become an acupuncturist;
May not have a household member who is an acupuncturist or in training to become an acupuncturist;
May not participate or ever have participated in a commercial or professional field related to acupuncture;
May not have a household member who participates in a commercial or professional field related to acupuncture; and
May not have had within 2 years before appointment a substantial financial interest in a person regulated by the Board.
